Incorporate delimiters such as <>, <tag></tag>, or '' in the original prompt to highlight key concepts, tasks, or entities. This helps to visually distinguish important elements and provides clarity to the model about the specific focus of the prompt.

Here are examples demonstrating how to apply this principle:

[original]
Create a step-by-step guide on how to meditate for beginners, highlighting its benefits for mental well-being.
[improved]
Create a step-by-step guide on how to <meditate> for beginners, highlighting its benefits for mental well-being.

========
